    </p>
    <p>
        I completed my PhD in <a class="footer__link" href="https://psychology.yale.edu/graduate/overview-program" target="_blank">Psychology at Yale University</a>.  I worked primarily in Brian Scholl's <a class="footer__link" href="https://perception.yale.edu/" target="_blank" >Perception and Cognition lab</a>, and also collaborated with Ilker Yildirim's <a class="footer__link" href="http://cncl.yale.edu/" target="_blank" >Cognitive & Neural Computation lab</a>. Previously, I worked with Michael (Mike) McCloskey in the <a class="footer__link" href="https://sites.krieger.jhu.edu/mccloskey-lab/people/" target="_blank" >Cognitive Neuroscience Lab</a> at Johns Hopkins.
